{
  "id": 6242687411945472,
  "name": "Document Policy in Dedicated Workers",
  "summary": "Enables document-policy in Dedicated Workers.\n\nThis enables developers to use Document Policy feature, such as performance or security controls in workers, instead of being limited to the main document. By extending policy enforcement to dedicated workers, developers gain more consistent behavior across threads and better control over worker capabilities in complex web applications.",
