  "rollout_plan_displayname": "Will ship enabled for all users",
  "motivation": "Dedicated Workers are commonly used to move logic off the main thread, but Document Policy currently applies only to the main document. This creates inconsistent enforcement when code is refactored into workers, and document‑level constraints no longer apply. Extending Document Policy to Dedicated Workers preserves consistent behavior across execution contexts and avoids policy gaps when using workers.",
